  <system:String x:Key="context.part.generateharmonies">生成和声...</system:String>

  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.about.close">关闭</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.about.contributors.embedded">正在显示内嵌的贡献者列表。</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.about.contributors.intro">以下人员为 GitHub 上原始 OpenUtau 仓库做出了贡献。OpenUtau Lunai 建立在他们的工作之上。感谢所有列出的贡献者！</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.about.contributors.loading">正在从 GitHub 加载贡献者...</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.about.contributors.title">贡献者</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.about.contributors.unavailable">无法加载贡献者。请检查网络连接后重试。</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.about.contributors.updated">已从 GitHub 更新贡献者列表。</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.about.contributors.upstream">OpenUtau ({0})</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.about.github.lunai">GitHub 上的 OpenUtau Lunai</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.about.github.upstream">GitHub 上的 OpenUtau</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.about.license">OpenUtau 与 OpenUtau Lunai 均为采用 MIT 许可证的免费开源软件。</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.about.lunai.message">您正在运行 OpenUtau Lunai，这是一个旨在让 DiffSinger 更易用、更愉快的分支。经典 UTAU 音源以及 OpenUtau 已支持的其他类型音源均可照常使用。此外还包含许多尚未发布或合并到原始 OpenUtau 的上游拉取请求中的功能。</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.about.message">OpenUtau 致力于成为面向 UTAU 社区的开源编辑环境，提供现代化的使用体验与智能音韵支持。欢迎访问我们的 GitHub。</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.about.upstream.message">OpenUtau 致力于成为面向 UTAU 社区的开源编辑环境，提供现代化的使用体验与智能音韵支持。</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.dropproject.caption">打开或导入工程</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.dropproject.import">导入音轨</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.dropproject.message">要打开拖入的工程文件，还是将其音轨导入到当前工程？</system:String>
