  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.reportissue.email.description">如问题难以复现，请写信给我们并附上日志。</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.reportissue.email.title">电子邮件</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.reportissue.email.write">撰写邮件</system:String>
  <system:String x:Key="dialogs.reportissue.message">请告诉我们出了什么问题。建议优先使用 Discord #help，以便我们尽快回复；有帮助时请附上日志文件。也可以通过电子邮件联系我们。</system:String>

